    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Preposition 'On/Above' - فوق",
          "arabic": "فوق"
        },
        "text": "The preposition 'فوق' (fūq) means 'on' or 'above'. It's used to describe something being on the surface of another object or directly above it.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "الكتاب فوق الطبلة.",
            "english": "The book is on the table.",
            "transliteration": "El-ktāb fūq eṭ-ṭbla."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الكرة فوق الصندوق.",
            "english": "The ball is on the box.",
            "transliteration": "El-kora fūq eṣ-ṣendūq."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Preposition 'Under' - تحت",
          "arabic": "تحت"
        },
        "text": "The preposition 'تحت' (taḥt) means 'under' or 'below'. It's the opposite of 'فوق' and indicates something is beneath another object.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "القط تحت الكرسي.",
            "english": "The cat is under the chair.",
            "transliteration": "El-qaṭṭ taḥt el-korsi."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "الستيلو تحت البيرو.",
            "english": "The pen is under the desk.",
            "transliteration": "Es-stīlo taḥt el-bīro."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Preposition 'In/At' - فـ",
          "arabic": "فـ"
        },
        "text": "The preposition 'فـ' (fī) means 'in' or 'at'. It indicates something is inside an enclosure or at a specific location.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "القهوة فـ الكاس.",
            "english": "The coffee is in the cup.",
            "transliteration": "El-qahwa fī el-kās."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "أنا فـ الدار.",
            "english": "I am at home.",
            "transliteration": "Ana fī ed-dār."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "المفاتح فـ المحفظة.",
            "english": "The keys are in the bag.",
            "transliteration": "El-mfāteḥ fī el-maḥfaḍa."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
